WEBVTT

00:01.520 --> 00:08.960
I am so very happy to see so many\h
Sahaja Yogis are here now in America.

00:12.240 --> 00:19.360
And the program we have had\h
the other day showed us clearly\h\h

00:20.640 --> 00:27.200
that Sahaja Yoga is getting very popular\h
and the way people got their realization\h\h

00:28.080 --> 00:38.720
in five minutes also showed that now we have\h
touched that area of seekers who are honest\h\h

00:39.760 --> 00:43.840
and who are of a very high level in spirituality.

00:47.680 --> 00:52.560
You are the ones who are the first Sahaja\h
Yogis we should say or the foundation\h\h

00:52.560 --> 01:03.040
of the Sahaja Yoga in America and thus we\h
have to understand our own responsibility.

01:04.960 --> 01:11.840
As it is Vishuddhi Chakra is\h
responsible for the whole world.

01:13.040 --> 01:24.720
But the people in Vishuddhi Chakra have to be\h
like Ganas, they have to be very responsible,\h\h

01:25.440 --> 01:30.000
extremely, much more than any\h
other country in the whole world.

01:32.400 --> 01:42.080
And the problem is somehow I found, I don’t\h
know about the future, that, that sense of\h\h

01:42.080 --> 01:50.720
responsibility yet not felt among Sahaja Yogis\h
that they are responsible for the whole world;\h\h

01:52.080 --> 01:58.480
not only for America or only for\h
New York or only for Yonkers.

02:00.560 --> 02:04.240
Sitting down here you are\h
responsible for the whole world.

02:06.240 --> 02:14.240
If you understand this that the main quality\h
of Vishuddhi Chakra is responsibility,\h\h

02:15.040 --> 02:16.640
I always say, “It’s on my shoulder.

02:17.600 --> 02:19.680
I take it on my shoulder”, meaning what?

02:20.480 --> 02:22.480
That I take the responsibility,\h\h

02:26.640 --> 02:36.000
but this sense of responsibility\h
has to come to you very clearly.

02:36.000 --> 02:41.360
I felt America is so far\h
away but if they could come\h\h

02:42.160 --> 02:50.560
and see in Russia how the Russians are\h
behaving towards Sahaja Yoga they’ll be amazed.

02:51.680 --> 02:54.960
I’ve been coming to America since so many years.

02:56.480 --> 02:58.960
Perhaps we should say this is\h
the first country I visited.

03:00.080 --> 03:06.160
But here the sense of responsibility\h
for Sahaja Yoga has not grown.

03:06.720 --> 03:12.080
While in a country like Russia and Eastern\h
blocks I’ve been only four years there hardly\h\h

03:12.800 --> 03:17.920
and you should see it how they feel responsible.

03:17.920 --> 03:22.880
Now in Russia, Sahaja Yoga\h
has spread upto Siberia.

03:24.720 --> 03:31.840
Now in Siberia they don’t live for\h
themselves only or for their Ashram.

03:32.640 --> 03:36.120
There they have got a place called Novosibirsk,\h\h

03:37.680 --> 03:44.640
which is mostly inhabited by scientists\h
because so many scientists were thrown away\h\h

03:45.680 --> 03:54.240
by Czars and later on by the communists\h
and were exiled into that place.

03:55.520 --> 04:00.560
Now these people sitting there tried\h
to find out what is spirituality?

04:02.000 --> 04:03.760
How do we get to spirituality?

04:04.400 --> 04:10.400
What is the way we can be our spiritual being?

04:12.240 --> 04:18.880
No quarrel, no fights, no stupid things\h
that people do, no domination, no ego.

04:23.760 --> 04:30.640
I was there only about a week back I should\h
say, more than a week and last day before going,\h\h

04:32.720 --> 04:34.160
there came a scientist.

04:36.400 --> 04:44.080
His eyes really were just like\h
ocean, were absolutely beautiful\h\h

04:46.480 --> 04:50.640
and he was supposed to be one of\h
the greatest scientist of Russia\h\h

04:51.760 --> 04:58.800
having a very big job of his own and he\h
didn’t talk about too much to others.

04:59.440 --> 05:00.800
He just wanted to see me.

05:02.400 --> 05:08.160
When he came he just took my\h
hand and kissed it, bowed to me.

05:08.880 --> 05:13.280
I saw in his eyes ocean of spirituality, ocean.

05:14.880 --> 05:18.160
He must have been about\h
thirty-five or forty years of age.

05:18.960 --> 05:22.000
Can’t say his age because he\h
was so much shining and bright\h\h

05:23.360 --> 05:27.520
and he told me, “I know everything about Mother”.

05:28.480 --> 05:29.440
I said, “What do you know?”

05:30.560 --> 05:34.400
“That you are the incarnation of\h
God on this Earth to save us”.

05:36.320 --> 05:37.840
“How did you find out?”

05:38.960 --> 05:42.880
He said, “I have made a machine by\h
which I can measure energy fields,\h\h

05:44.400 --> 05:47.200
of course I can’t measure your energy field.

05:47.200 --> 05:53.920
But I took a small photograph of your\h
and measured the energy field and I found\h\h

05:53.920 --> 05:59.520
it was seven hundred raised to power some\h
millions and then raised to power some billions”.

05:59.520 --> 06:01.200
That’s why I don’t understand his calculation.

06:02.880 --> 06:07.200
Just imagine, and he created\h\h

06:10.480 --> 06:20.000
the whole idea of his proposed experiments for\h
which he had come to take permission from Me.

06:20.000 --> 06:22.720
He said, “You just touch this\h
glass Mother, just touch it”.

06:24.400 --> 06:25.520
And he had brought a machine.

06:26.640 --> 06:29.920
I touched the glass and machine\h
went on revolving like that.

06:33.440 --> 06:34.880
I was myself surprised.

06:36.240 --> 06:38.480
He said, “Just touching the glass it’s happening”.

06:39.920 --> 06:42.400
He had a machine with him,\h
a little machine he said.

06:42.400 --> 06:45.280
“This is portable”, he said.

06:45.280 --> 06:48.160
So I said, “What is the permission you want?”

06:48.160 --> 06:50.080
He said, “I want to use your photograph\h\h

06:52.080 --> 07:00.720
on a Satellite and from the Satellite I want to\h
project your photograph through electromagnetic\h\h

07:00.720 --> 07:10.240
force and wherever in the Global region it\h
will be put, you will see it will change.

07:10.240 --> 07:16.400
It will change people, it will change all flora,\h
fauna and also ecological problems will be solved.

07:17.200 --> 07:18.720
Will you give me permission for that”.

07:18.720 --> 07:19.840
I said, “Of course why not?”

07:23.840 --> 07:28.880
The level of scientist in that country\h
is so great, here I don’t think we can\h\h

07:28.880 --> 07:34.320
get hold of any scientist because their\h
ego is keeping them hanging in the air.

07:37.920 --> 07:44.240
The another thing, which I was surprised,\h
that in Novosibirsk, where a Yogi told them\h\h

07:44.960 --> 07:49.840
that Mother has told us that in our brain\h
there are ‘peethas’ of these charkas.

07:51.680 --> 07:58.400
They were so much surprised they said, “We\h
can verify, we have machines to verify”.

07:59.680 --> 08:00.720
So they called Dr.

08:00.720 --> 08:03.120
Khan and when Dr.

08:03.120 --> 08:08.160
Khan went there, he was\h
amazed, they had a machine.

08:10.240 --> 08:15.600
So he said, “Now let us put\h
attention to Shri Mataji”.

08:15.600 --> 08:17.280
The whole brain became reddish.

08:18.640 --> 08:23.680
Then “Let us put attention to\h
heart”; here it became a red spot.

08:24.720 --> 08:26.800
Then to Mooladhara, was here.

08:26.800 --> 08:29.680
Then to Nabhi, on both the\h
places; then to Vishuddhi.

08:30.720 --> 08:31.520
It was proved.

08:33.440 --> 08:35.280
What I have said they have proved it.

08:39.600 --> 08:42.960
And so many Americans are trying\h
to get them to this country.

08:43.760 --> 08:45.200
They say, “We don’t want to come.

08:45.200 --> 08:50.000
We don’t want to do any more Science, we\h
want to do Meta-science, spirituality”.

08:50.000 --> 08:55.040
There are two hundred and fifty scientists\h
in Novosibirsk where I could not go\h\h

08:56.480 --> 08:57.680
because we had a puja.

09:00.640 --> 09:07.840
Now see the difference, here I come\h
there’s quarrels between husband – wife;\h\h

09:08.400 --> 09:10.640
then it’s a father – mother.

09:12.160 --> 09:15.360
All such petty nonsensical things are going on.

09:19.920 --> 09:28.000
So your own brothers and sisters in\h
another country are doing so much of\h\h

09:32.240 --> 09:36.000
experimentation, spreading of Sahaja Yoga.

09:36.880 --> 09:39.680
Imagine how will I go to Siberia, out of question.

09:41.520 --> 09:44.960
But from Siberia I don’t\h
know how many thousands came.

09:49.280 --> 09:55.120
They are all well-educated, very well\h
equipped, extremely well behaved.

09:58.720 --> 10:02.080
In their style, in their behavior you see that\h\h

10:03.600 --> 10:08.680
there is such a lot of\h
spirituality already built in.

10:10.320 --> 10:18.640
When I went to Ukraine; Ukraine is a place where\h
they had this, you know, Chernobyl problem.

10:19.600 --> 10:23.360
First time when I had gone there were\h
people, who had come to my program.

10:24.080 --> 10:28.480
They had their fingers joint like this,\h
noses turned like this, all kinds of things.

10:30.080 --> 10:32.800
And the legs and feet were in a very funny way.

10:34.560 --> 10:38.160
With all that, they came to the program\h\h

10:39.360 --> 10:45.040
and this time that hall was so full there were\h
at least ten times more people than we are here,\h\h

10:45.040 --> 10:52.400
maybe more and outside were standing, they\h
couldn’t get in, they are sitting in the passages.

10:52.400 --> 10:56.640
They were three tier, on\h
the ground and three more.

10:56.640 --> 11:05.760
Everything filled to a inch and I\h
was amazed at their spirituality.

11:05.760 --> 11:09.120
Everyone got realization in five minutes.

11:11.920 --> 11:15.440
What a level of people, what a level.

11:15.440 --> 11:18.880
But then I found out that in Ukraine\h\h

11:20.320 --> 11:24.960
they already had the knowledge of\h
Kundalini and of the Primordial Mother.

11:24.960 --> 11:31.280
They call Her ‘Aditi’, in India also we call Her\h
‘Aditi’ and they used to make paintings of her.

11:33.280 --> 11:39.760
Then they had paintings made of Agnya\h
Chakra, of Mooladhara, very clear.

11:41.440 --> 11:45.800
In those days before Christ, three\h
thousand years before Christ.

11:46.880 --> 11:56.840
So basically in them from where,\h
somewhere, this knowledge had come.

11:58.240 --> 12:02.000
You are very advanced people here, supposed to.

12:03.520 --> 12:11.840
You are very well equipped and people\h
think Americans are the top for everything.

12:15.040 --> 12:18.800
But look at these people\h
from Ukraine and from Russia.

12:19.920 --> 12:24.080
They were worshiping the Primordial Mother\h\h

12:24.080 --> 12:28.240
three thousand before Christ and when\h
Christianity came, they suppressed it.

12:28.800 --> 12:30.240
All clearly written down\h\h

12:34.240 --> 12:38.000
and when people wrote about it also, these\h\h

12:38.000 --> 12:45.520
Christians there, they were called as orthodox\h
Christian, they tried to kill them, arrest them.

12:47.120 --> 12:48.480
Despite all those\h\h

12:50.480 --> 12:58.400
problems they stuck on and I was surprised that\h
even today there are books and magazines about it.

13:04.560 --> 13:09.920
So I was thinking somebody like Macchindranath\h
who went all over the world, must have gone\h\h

13:09.920 --> 13:15.840
with his disciples Gorakhnath, because they were\h
Nath Panthis, they knew about Kundalini and all.

13:15.840 --> 13:24.382
But actually they have shown the ‘Aditi’,\h
the Mother with the Kundalini in a stomach.

13:24.382 --> 13:27.360
Can you imagine?

13:27.360 --> 13:34.160
All these things were done long\h
time back and that’s why basically\h\h

13:36.160 --> 13:38.000
they are very spiritual people.

13:39.200 --> 13:48.640
Firstly they are very introspective and very\h
spiritual and all the time they are asking “Mother\h\h

13:49.920 --> 13:51.360
are we going to be all right?

13:52.480 --> 13:53.360
Are we all right?

13:54.400 --> 13:57.840
Have we really taken our ascent?” Like that\h\h

13:57.840 --> 14:02.880
those questions, which were absolutely\h
different from what you see in the West.

14:07.760 --> 14:12.880
In whatever field they are; if he is\h
a doctor he’ll try to find something.

14:13.600 --> 14:18.080
A dentist, they’ll try to find\h
something, related to Sahaja Yoga\h\h

14:19.040 --> 14:22.320
and they say, “There are so many\h
coincidences that you cannot explain.

14:23.840 --> 14:28.800
How this has worked out, how?” So I said,\h
“What did you do?” He said, “We just desire\h\h

14:29.600 --> 14:32.480
that we should now try to propagate Sahaja Yoga\h\h

14:33.200 --> 14:43.360
and to analyze it and put, put it on such\h
a concrete way that nobody can doubt it.

14:43.360 --> 14:44.640
No Scientist can doubt it”.

14:46.480 --> 14:50.960
So we are at that level to\h
see somebody so much higher\h\h

14:53.360 --> 14:58.720
and then we have also understanding\h
how we can rise upto that point?

15:00.480 --> 15:01.840
How we have to work it out?

15:03.040 --> 15:11.840
Now the pettiness with which we suffer can come\h
in many categories but is nothing but stupidity.

15:13.040 --> 15:17.840
One of them is that, this idea of leadership;\h\h

15:19.600 --> 15:23.360
which is greatest stupidity\h
you could ever think of.

15:25.200 --> 15:27.680
I am just befooling you by\h
saying “You are a leader.

15:27.680 --> 15:28.400
You are a leader”.

15:28.400 --> 15:35.600
Nothing it’s just a myth,\h
you don’t believe me in that.

15:37.360 --> 15:40.880
If I call you the leader, you must\h
know that Mother is trying to test you\h\h

15:42.400 --> 15:51.360
and others also those who are trying this power\h
game of becoming leaders, nothing at the back.

15:51.360 --> 15:58.080
There is no one who you can really say is\h
the leader of Sahaja Yoga except that I\h\h

15:58.720 --> 16:02.160
had to have some people to\h
communicate so we call them leaders.

16:03.040 --> 16:05.280
It doesn’t mean that if they become leaders,\h\h

16:06.160 --> 16:16.800
they go to heaven; they will get a right\h
royal reception, nothing like that.

16:16.800 --> 16:19.760
All will be going in the same manner.

16:21.360 --> 16:23.760
See this is all created by Maya.

16:25.680 --> 16:36.160
Now people are striving to become\h
leader, and I really feel like laughing.

16:36.160 --> 16:42.880
Those who will try are climbing\h
a mountain, which doesn’t exist.

16:46.960 --> 16:48.080
Where are you climbing?

16:48.640 --> 16:50.320
Where are you going?

16:50.320 --> 16:51.440
It doesn’t exist.

16:51.440 --> 16:53.440
There’s no mountain, it’s\h
all straightforward road.

16:57.840 --> 17:01.280
So this is also a sign of complete stupidity.

17:02.960 --> 17:06.240
Are we to say that all the\h
stupids are born in this country?

17:08.800 --> 17:15.680
Are we to feel that all stupidity has trickled\h
down to this country through Hudson River?

17:17.600 --> 17:23.840
Are we to believe that all\h
intelligence has vanished into ego?

17:28.000 --> 17:34.160
Once you realize it is stupidity, it’s best to\h
stand before the mirror and make fun of yourself.

17:36.240 --> 17:42.000
Also I’ve noticed with all the writers of\h
Russia, they’ve been very introspective.

17:43.680 --> 17:47.040
Even a hero will think ten times\h
“Why I am loving this lady?

17:47.040 --> 17:52.400
Why I am doing this?” Even the woman if she’s\h
in love she’ll think, “Why am I doing that?

17:52.400 --> 17:54.160
Should I do it or not?

17:54.160 --> 17:55.280
It’s proper or not?

17:56.400 --> 17:59.840
Is it something in my head that\h
is making me do it?” You see,\h\h

17:59.840 --> 18:04.160
absolutely clearly they go\h
on introspecting themselves.

18:04.720 --> 18:07.640
Even now I find the Russians are like that.

18:08.160 --> 18:10.640
So we have to now start a new tradition.

18:12.080 --> 18:14.320
In that tradition, we have to introspect.

18:17.520 --> 18:18.720
Introspect yourself.

18:19.760 --> 18:32.320
This another way is you shouldn’t\h
try to see the defects of others\h\h

18:32.320 --> 18:34.000
but to see what’s wrong with you?

18:37.040 --> 18:37.760
Where do you fail?

18:38.960 --> 18:39.600
Why do you fail?

18:40.480 --> 18:42.240
Why you cannot propagate Sahaja Yoga?

18:43.200 --> 18:45.120
What is the reason to it?

18:45.120 --> 18:46.080
What has failed you?

18:50.480 --> 18:57.840
Because it’s only possible when you think you\h
are responsible, not leader but responsible.

19:00.320 --> 19:04.080
This is the country where we’ve\h
had greatest fights for leadership\h\h

19:04.720 --> 19:09.920
and all leaders have now jumped into river Hudson.

19:09.920 --> 19:12.640
So this kind of stupid ideas should be given up\h\h

19:13.280 --> 19:16.320
and we should introspect to\h
see how much stupid we are.

19:19.920 --> 19:29.040
I had started believing that the special blessing\h
of Maya is on Americans that they are all stupid.

19:29.840 --> 19:34.800
I used to really, I used to think,\h
I must confess, in a beginning.

19:35.680 --> 19:39.840
Then I met you all and I\h
realized it’s not that bad.

19:51.760 --> 19:54.320
Because I met so many important people,\h\h

19:55.360 --> 19:58.480
Ambassadors, this and that\h
and all that, in England.

19:59.200 --> 20:01.280
I used to wonder what’s wrong with them.

20:03.280 --> 20:08.240
They used to behave like young\h
boys of twenty years you see.

20:08.240 --> 20:12.400
In Hindi we call it ‘gadha pachchsi’,\h
means at twenty-five you are a donkey.

20:15.440 --> 20:20.080
And the way they used to pass jokes\h
and I say they have no dignity,\h\h

20:20.080 --> 20:24.480
nothing; such high positions they\h
are having what do they talk about?

20:25.680 --> 20:27.600
And they would stand out by that you know?

20:27.600 --> 20:29.280
They said, “Ah we’re very smart” you know?

20:30.000 --> 20:33.280
They would wink at everyone, they\h
would do all kinds of nonsensical\h\h

20:33.280 --> 20:38.080
thing which normally a twenty year\h
boy might do anywhere once in a while.

20:38.800 --> 20:39.920
But they were all like that.

20:41.680 --> 20:45.440
They thought they were very young\h
and they would walk you see with very\h\h

20:45.440 --> 20:48.400
great smartness you see like young boys.

20:49.120 --> 20:58.160
To them it should be very fast and like you see a\h
bowler is about to bowl or some sort of a thing.

20:59.120 --> 21:06.720
It was really unbelievable that these people\h
occupy such high position in the government.

21:06.720 --> 21:08.560
How could they be so irresponsible?

21:10.880 --> 21:16.640
But when I met you all then I really felt\h
that no no there are many good people also.

21:19.280 --> 21:25.520
This comparison you can today also\h
see between you and these people.

21:26.880 --> 21:29.840
They’ll argue for anything.

21:30.560 --> 21:33.440
They’ll talk about anything like\h
for Freud they were fighting.

21:35.520 --> 21:37.680
Freud’s told us something very new.

21:39.280 --> 21:41.680
So I’ve written in my book, so I said, “All right\h\h

21:42.640 --> 21:47.040
you have eaten all kinds of food before\h
but you have not eaten the table.

21:47.040 --> 21:48.320
What about eating the table?”\h\h

21:49.920 --> 21:57.840
So everything absurd, everything vulgar,\h
everything low level were justified.

21:59.120 --> 22:00.000
I don’t blame him.

22:04.800 --> 22:10.160
All these stupid people were\h
born here and they wrote books.

22:11.040 --> 22:14.640
They were the ones who were Generals.

22:16.240 --> 22:17.600
They were in-charge.

22:17.600 --> 22:18.880
I mean I can’t understand.

22:21.040 --> 22:26.000
You see this fellow Nought.

22:26.000 --> 22:29.280
You can one minute you look at him\h
and you will know he’s a lunatic\h\h

22:31.280 --> 22:36.880
and they gave him so much time so much\h
explanation; I mean I can’t understand.

22:38.960 --> 22:47.120
And the idea about spirituality is like\h
somebody comes and tells you something absurd.

22:47.120 --> 22:51.760
It’s new, it’s new, so do it.

22:51.760 --> 22:55.590
Now they say that you shave your head;\h
all right, they shave their head.

22:55.590 --> 22:58.640
They’ll say no “you grow\h
your hair” and they’ll grow.

22:58.640 --> 23:02.000
As if they have no personality of their own.

23:03.040 --> 23:05.840
They don’t think much about themselves.

23:05.840 --> 23:07.840
They have no respect of themselves.

23:08.960 --> 23:14.000
Even in those parties they used to tell me\h
“Ah have you been to this Guru?” I said,\h\h

23:14.000 --> 23:18.240
“No I am sorry, I’ve not”\h
Nowadays its bargain better do it.

23:20.000 --> 23:26.240
Level of understanding of spirituality was also\h
so low of these people who were so highly placed\h\h

23:28.160 --> 23:35.840
and I was really I was amazed how could\h
they do such things with such big position.

23:36.480 --> 23:38.480
There was one fellow who was quite highly placed\h\h

23:39.920 --> 23:43.520
he used to always look out for\h
me, whenever there was a party.

23:44.800 --> 23:45.280
So C.P.

23:45.280 --> 23:50.240
said, “Why does he look out for you?”\h
I said you know he wants to eat a lot\h\h

23:50.240 --> 23:55.120
and here the food they serve in\h
England is not sufficient for him.

23:55.840 --> 23:59.280
So he sit next to me so he\h
can share all my food you see.

23:59.280 --> 24:00.400
That’s why he always there.

24:01.040 --> 24:02.000
I eat very little.

24:02.960 --> 24:05.040
So, so much interest in food.

24:06.480 --> 24:09.440
Then when I was not there he\h
would go and sit with C.P.

24:09.440 --> 24:11.840
because He knew the secret He\h
used to pass His food to him.

24:13.040 --> 24:20.160
So much interest in food and himself was in a such\h
a big position and what was he boasting about?

24:20.800 --> 24:25.400
That I come on a bicycle on a half pant to office.

24:25.400 --> 24:28.400
So I said, “Why do you go on a half pant?”

