months you’ll be all right”.

26:56.080 --> 26:59.440
So all such bombastic talking those people who do,\h\h

27:00.400 --> 27:06.720
you should just know I am telling you\h
certified lunatics or certified fools.

27:10.800 --> 27:22.840
And once this goes, this stupidity into your\h
head you will be no more a Sahaja Yogi, no more.

27:24.160 --> 27:30.640
Whole spirituality will come out\h
