27:32.480 --> 27:34.160
Anyone who boasts like that\h\h

27:36.080 --> 27:42.720
is worse but even if you think like\h
that is no good, not on a proper lines.

27:45.760 --> 27:50.720
So because of this ego you don’t\h
understand your responsibility.

