37:46.080 --> 37:48.320
He said, “What is cow?”

37:48.320 --> 37:51.040
“It’s very big animal compared to you”.

37:51.040 --> 37:52.320
“I can also become big.

37:52.320 --> 37:59.600
Why not I will” and starts\h
growing, growing till he burst out.

38:00.560 --> 38:03.040
So this is what it is we have to understand\h\h

38:03.760 --> 38:10.720
that this ego business is the real,\h
real, real problem of America.

38:17.280 --> 38:20.880
So now you have to surrender.

38:21.920 --> 38:23.760
